result.name: Tom N Toms Coffee

reviews.text:
Great place to get a coffee or one of those fruit-infused teas, and sit and get some work done on one of their sofas.

Excellent service!
Nice place to take a rest with beautiful Kowloon garden view
Coffee quality is the best among coffee chain shops.  Delivery to table top is default service.
I like the food more then the coffee...toast r super yummy...

The food is a bit overpriced imho, but at least it's tasty. The coffee is really good and the cafe is a pretty good place to chill. the lack of power outlets mean you're not getting the crappy student crowd that buys one drink but takes up 3+ tables. And the view from the patio when it's open is good. Not many places can offer this view at such a reasonable price.

result.name: The ONE

reviews.text: Yes, it is another building for shopping and dinning. Once you jump on here, you can spend all your day long here shopping luxury goods, watching movies, and enjoying and dinning from luxury high end cuisine to budget restaurant and even sweety desert. And there are supermarket and small souvenirs shops too. There are some shops where you may experience only this place.
most convenient shopping mall with great restaurants

Very nice song mall with a wide array of styles of shops and levels of cost. It also has a cinema inside, several floors for restaurants and tea/dessert options, as well as four luxury restaurants with harbour views at the very top floors. Always a pleasant place and an option when around TST.
One stop for shopping and restaurants for every taste and any budget

Facing both nathan road and granville road corner. Nearest MTR station is Tsim Sha Tsui station Exit B2.
Please like my review if its helpful. 🙏

result.name: TOM N TOMS COFFEE

reviews.text:
很久沒有去這家買飲品 這次去到不太多人
有位置可以坐 所以就買杯飲品去吧🤔🤔

我想點茶飲 但全部都沒有😑為什麼會這樣
下午茶時間還未到就賣光了? 是準備不足嗎？
唯有買梳打飲吧 等了十分鐘終於有得取飲品

·柚子湯娒梳打 HKD$36
沒有杯蓋[笑哭] 味道不過不失吧 不太甜剛好吧
唯一不好的是 會員有送餐服務 不是說沒有
令人感覺有點差吧 為什麼會待遇不相同🌚🌚

The One Hea時間等人最好cafe，坐得舒服，位都算多，食件多士加杯咖啡大概80蚊左右，仲有連得到但慢過4G嘅WiFi，可以一試！
*個忌廉焦糖多士幾正，推薦！

더원3층에위치한탐탐
공간도좋구테라스바로옆에
담배도필수있어서남자들한테는
정말좋은장소입니다
몰안에있어서시원하구요.
그냥말그대로
탐탐고대로느낌입니다
무료와이파이있어요조금느리지만
朋友敍舊十分好，有充足空間。飲品種類多，食物也很好。

Great place to get a coffee or one of those fruit-infused teas, and sit and get some work done on one of their sofas.

Excellent service!
